OL,3,CPickford says England squad 'ready for
OL,4,Cpenalties' ahead of Argentina clash
OL,6,FEngland goalkeeper Jordan Pickford has
OL,7,Fsaid the Three Lions are "ready for
OL,8,Fanything", including penalties, ahead
OL,9,Fof the squad's World Cup semi-final
OL,10,Fclash with Argentina on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThomas Tuchel's side have the chance
OL,13,Fto become the nation's first men's
OL,14,Fteam to reach the final since Sir Alf
OL,15,FRamsey's heroes lifted the trophy in
OL,16,F1966.
OL,18,FWorld champions Argentina stand in
OL,19,Ftheir way, as the eyes of the nation
OL,20,Fwill be on Atlanta for what is sure to
OL,21,Fbe an electric encounter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
