OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784038719
OL,3,CPickford says England squad 'ready for
OL,4,Cpenalties' ahead of Argentina clash
OL,6,F"It's just a game of football,"
OL,7,FPickford said when asked about the
OL,8,Fpolitics behind the England-Argentina
OL,9,Fmatch
OL,11,FPickford said Argentina is a "top
OL,12,Fnation", but the England team has a
OL,13,F"togetherness" that will get them
OL,14,Fthrough.
OL,16,F"Everyone will talk about Messi
OL,17,Fbecause he's one of the GOATs
OL,18,F(greatest of all time) of the game,"
OL,19,FPickford said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784038719
OL,3,CPickford says England squad 'ready for
OL,4,Cpenalties' ahead of Argentina clash
OL,6,F"But you can't look past the ability
OL,7,Fand the talent we've got in the squad
OL,8,F` going forward, defensively,
OL,9,Ftogetherness. We've got it all there
OL,10,Fand that's what we need to put on show
OL,11,Fon Wednesday."
OL,13,FEngland against Argentina holds a lot
OL,14,Fof history for a variety of reasons,
OL,15,Fincluding Diego Maradona's 'Hand of
OL,16,FGod' in 1986.
OL,18,FBut against that backdrop, Pickford
OL,19,Fsaid it was "just a game of football".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784038719
OL,3,CPickford says England squad 'ready for
OL,4,Cpenalties' ahead of Argentina clash
OL,6,F"I think it's just solely focus on us
OL,7,Fas England now and us being at our
OL,8,Fbest to beat another top nation,"
OL,9,FPickford said.
OL,11,F"It's us against them to get a place
OL,12,Fin the final, and it's a game of
OL,13,Ffootball. 90 minutes, 120, penalties.
OL,15,F"We're ready for anything, and it's us
OL,16,Fagainst them and it's about who comes
OL,17,Fout on top. We're fully prepared for
OL,18,Fthat."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]sD@AOUwD@AOUzD@FO]
